thread.title_full: Country Attire Ltd. (www.countryattire.com) reviewed by A Crawford

author: A Crawford
title: A Crawford
text: House of Fraser were out of stock as were Barbour themselves. Googled the Barbour jacket, found these guys had it in stock and took a punt on them. Can't fault them and I will without reservation search them again when I buy more Barbour products. Shop with confidence, 5*
